<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>战区</title><link>https://www.twz.com</link><description>防御世界的强大进攻。</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 02:52:58 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>海军陆战队展示新型巡航导弹 MV-75 倾转旋翼机概念</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/new-cruise-missile-armed-mv-75-tiltrotor-concept-for-the-marines-shown-off</link><description>&lt;p&gt;海军陆战队表示，在谈到 AH-1 和 UH-1 直升机的潜在替代品时，“一切都已摆在桌面上”。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/new-cruise-missile-armed-mv-75-tiltrotor-concept-for-the-marines-shown-off"&gt;为海军陆战队展示的新型巡航导弹武装 MV-75 倾转旋翼机概念&lt;/a&gt;后首次出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Apr 2026 21:46:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/new-cruise-missile-armed-mv-75-tiltrotor-concept-for-the-marines-shown-off</guid></item><item><title>基于罗宾逊 R66 和贝尔 505 的轻型无人货运直升机争夺美国海军陆战队合同</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/light-uncrewed-cargo-helicopters-based-on-robinson-r66-and-bell-505-compete-usmc-contract</link><description>&lt;p&gt;两种经过验证的商用旋翼设计的改编正在争夺美国海军陆战队自主补给车辆的需求。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/light-uncrewed-cargo-helicopters-based-on-robinson-r66-and-bell-505-compete-usmc-contract"&gt;基于罗宾逊 R66 和贝尔 505 的轻型无人货运直升机竞争 USMC 合同后的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Apr 2026 18:09:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/light-uncrewed-cargo-helicopters-based-on-robinson-r66-and-bell-505-compete-usmc-contract</guid></item><item><title>尽管“战略暂停”，海军今年仍在推动新型 AARGM-ER 雷达破坏导弹的部署</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/navy-still-pushing-to-field-new-air-defense-busting-missile-this-year-despite-strategic-pause</link><description>&lt;p&gt;美国海军预计 AGM-88G AARGM-ER 将于 9 月份投入使用，尽管他们没有计划在下一财年购买任何一款。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;尽管“战略&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;暂停&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/navy-still-pushing-to-field-new-air-defense-busting-missile-this-year-despite-strategic-pause"&gt;”，后海军今年仍在推动新型 AARGM-ER 雷达破坏导弹的部署&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Apr 2026 16:05:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/navy-still-pushing-to-field-new-air-defense-busting-missile-this-year-despite-strategic-pause</guid></item><item><title>MP7个人防卫武器在穿着定制西装的特工手中迅速走红</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/hks-mp7-personal-defense-weapon-just-went-viral-in-hands-of-tailored-suit-wearing-agent</link><description>&lt;p&gt;在一名枪手试图冲进白宫记者晚宴后，这位在压力下保持冷静的特工从一个隐蔽的背包里拿出了 MP7。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/hks-mp7-personal-defense-weapon-just-went-viral-in-hands-of-tailored-suit-wearing-agent"&gt;MP7个人防卫武器刚刚在穿着定制西装的特工手中疯传，&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Apr 2026 22:27:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/hks-mp7-personal-defense-weapon-just-went-viral-in-hands-of-tailored-suit-wearing-agent</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯隐形S-71K空射导弹的新细节</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/russias-stealthy-s-71k-air-launched-missile-seen-in-unprecedented-detail</link><description>&lt;p&gt;该导弹的目标是成为一种成本较低、但仍具有生存能力、可以大量制造的防区外武器选择。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/russias-stealthy-s-71k-air-launched-missile-seen-in-unprecedented-detail"&gt;俄罗斯隐形 S-71K 空射导弹以新细节&lt;/a&gt;亮相的帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Apr 2026 21:50:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/russias-stealthy-s-71k-air-launched-missile-seen-in-unprecedented-detail</guid></item><item><title>伊朗与美国开放海峡、结束战争的协议前景黯淡</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/prospects-dimming-on-iran-u-s-deal-to-open-strait-end-war</link><description>&lt;p&gt;德黑兰向华盛顿提出了一项新提议，但由于封锁旨在削弱伊朗的石油基础设施，该提议不太可能产生实质性进展。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/prospects-dimming-on-iran-u-s-deal-to-open-strait-end-war"&gt;伊朗与美国开放海峡协议前景黯淡，结束战争的帖子&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Apr 2026 19:37:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/prospects-dimming-on-iran-u-s-deal-to-open-strait-end-war</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰使用 AIM-120C-8 导弹的证据出现</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/evidence-of-ukraine-using-aim-120c-8-missiles-emerges</link><description>&lt;p&gt;残骸图像表明乌克兰正在部署接近顶级的 AIM-120C-8，可通过 F-16 和 NASAMS 发射器使用。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/evidence-of-ukraine-using-aim-120c-8-missiles-emerges"&gt;乌克兰使用 AIM-120C-8 导弹的后证据&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Apr 2026 17:38:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/evidence-of-ukraine-using-aim-120c-8-missiles-emerges</guid></item><item><title>罕见视频似乎显示一架苏联 Su-7 喷气式飞机投下核弹</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/rare-video-appears-to-show-a-soviet-su-7-jet-dropping-a-nuclear-bomb</link><description>&lt;p&gt;在一次非常不寻常的冷战演习中，一架苏联 Su-7 Fitter 攻击机在端到端测试中发射了一枚实弹战术核武器。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/rare-video-appears-to-show-a-soviet-su-7-jet-dropping-a-nuclear-bomb"&gt;罕见视频似乎显示一架苏联 Su-7 喷气式飞机投下核弹的帖子&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Apr 2026 18:08:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/rare-video-appears-to-show-a-soviet-su-7-jet-dropping-a-nuclear-bomb</guid></item><item><title>截至 2026 年 4 月 26 日的承运人追踪器</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/carrier-tracker-as-of-april-26-2026</link><description>&lt;p&gt;美国现在在美国中央司令部责任区拥有三个航母打击群，这是二十多年来的首次。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/carrier-tracker-as-of-april-26-2026"&gt;截至 2026 年 4 月 26 日的《承运商追踪》&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Apr 2026 17:35:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/carrier-tracker-as-of-april-26-2026</guid></item><item><title>地堡谈话：让我们谈谈本周我们做过和没有涵盖的所有事情</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-lets-talk-about-all-the-things-we-did-and-didnt-cover-this-week-189</link><description>&lt;p&gt;又一周了！&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-lets-talk-about-all-the-things-we-did-and-didnt-cover-this-week-189"&gt;《地堡谈话：让我们谈谈本周我们做过和没有涵盖的所有事情》&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Apr 2026 19:59:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-lets-talk-about-all-the-things-we-did-and-didnt-cover-this-week-189</guid></item></channel></rss>